{
  "uuid": "wlXF",
  "titre": "Limite d'une fonction définie sur $\\R^2$",
  "theme": "fonctions de plusieurs variables",
  "auteur": "",
  "date": "",
  "organisation": "AMSCC",
  "contenu": [
    {
      "type": "texte",
      "value": "<p>Soit <span class=\"math inline\">\\(f \\colon \\R^2 \\to \\R\\)</span>, <span\nclass=\"math display\">\\[(x,y) \\mapsto \\dfrac{x^2 y^2}{x^2 y^2 +\n(x-y)^2}\\]</span></p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "question",
      "value": "<p>Donner l’ensemble de définition de <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(f\\)</span>.</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": "<p>La fonction <span class=\"math inline\">\\(f\\)</span> est définie pour\ntout <span class=\"math inline\">\\((x,y)\\in \\R^2\\)</span> tels que <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(x^2 y^2 + (x-y)^2 \\neq 0\\)</span>. Or <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(x^2y^2 + (x-y)^2 = 0 \\iff xy = 0 \\text{ et } x=y\n\\iff x=y=0\\)</span> donc <span class=\"math inline\">\\(f\\)</span> est\ndéfinie sur <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\R^2 \\backslash\n\\{(0,0)\\}\\)</span>.</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "question",
      "value": "<p>Pour <span class=\"math inline\">\\(x\\)</span> fixé, calculer <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(g(x) = \\lim\\limits_{y \\to 0} f(x,y)\\)</span>.</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": "<p>Soit <span class=\"math inline\">\\(x \\in \\R\\)</span> : si <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(x=0\\)</span>, <span class=\"math inline\">\\(f(0,y) =\n0\\)</span> et si <span class=\"math inline\">\\(x \\neq 0\\)</span>, <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(f(x,y) \\xrightarrow[y \\to 0]{} \\frac{0}{x^2} =\n0\\)</span></p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "question",
      "value": "<p>Pour <span class=\"math inline\">\\(y\\)</span> fixé, calculer <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(h(y) = \\lim\\limits_{x \\to 0} f(x,y)\\)</span>.</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": "<p>De même, <span class=\"math inline\">\\(h(y) = 0\\)</span>.</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "question",
      "value": "<p>Calculer <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\lim\\limits_{x \\to 0}\ng(x)\\)</span>.</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": "<p>On en déduit que <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\lim\\limits_{x \\to 0}\ng(x) = 0\\)</span></p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "question",
      "value": "<p>Calculer <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\lim\\limits_{y \\to 0}\nh(y)\\)</span>.</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": "<p>De même <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\lim\\limits_{y \\to 0} h(y) =\n0\\)</span></p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "question",
      "value": "<p>La fonction <span class=\"math inline\">\\(f\\)</span> admet-elle une\nlimite quand <span class=\"math inline\">\\((x,y) \\to (0,0)\\)</span> ?</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": "<p>Non car <span class=\"math inline\">\\(f(x,x) = 1 \\xrightarrow[x \\to\n0]{} 1\\)</span> et <span class=\"math inline\">\\(f(x,0) = 0 \\xrightarrow[x\n\\to 0]{} 0 \\neq 1\\)</span> : on a deux chemins qui donnent deux limites\ndifférentes.</p>\n"
    }
  ]
}